## 5. System Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Ingestion["🔌 Data Ingestion Layer"]
        A1["Historical Shipments<br/>(ERP / TMS / WMS)"]
        A2["Carrier Bids<br/>(PDF / Excel / Email)"]
        A3["Market Intelligence<br/>(Fuel, CCFI, BDI, TAC Index)"]
        A4["Real-time Telemetry<br/>(GPS, AIS, FlightRadar, Rail IoT)"]
        A5["Port / Airport / Yard APIs<br/>(Congestion, Schedule Data)"]
    end

    subgraph Processing["⚙️ Processing Layer"]
        B1["Multi-Format Bid Parser<br/>(LLM + Mode-Specific Rules)"]
        B2["Data Pipeline + Feature Store<br/>(ETL per Mode)"]
        B3["Cross-Modal Normalizer<br/>($/ton-km Unification)"]
    end

    subgraph Intelligence["🧠 Four-Brain Intelligence Layer"]
        C0["Brain 0: Mode Selector<br/>Random Forest + SHAP<br/>(Road/Rail/Ocean/Air)"]
        C1["Brain 1: Analyst<br/>AHP-TOPSIS per Mode<br/>(Mode-Specific Scoring)"]
        C2["Brain 2: Predictor<br/>LightGBM / LSTM / Prophet<br/>(Mode-Specific Risk)"]
        C3["Brain 3: Strategist<br/>Multi-Objective MILP<br/>(Cross-Modal Optimization)"]
    end

    subgraph Learning["🔄 Learning Layer"]
        D1["Feedback Collector<br/>(Actual vs Predicted per Mode)"]
        D2["Mode-Stratified Bandits<br/>(Thompson Sampling)"]
        D3["Model Drift Monitor<br/>(Retrain Triggers)"]
    end

    subgraph Interface["💻 Multi-Modal Co-Pilot Interface"]
        E1["Mode Comparison Dashboard<br/>(Road vs Rail vs Ocean vs Air)"]
        E2["Carrier Scorecards per Mode<br/>(Lane-Level Rankings)"]
        E3["Multi-Modal What-If Simulator<br/>(Modal Shift Scenarios)"]
        E4["Explainability Panel<br/>(SHAP + Contrastive)"]
        E5["NL Co-Pilot Chat<br/>(Ask the Agent)"]
    end

    A1 & A2 & A3 & A4 & A5 --> B1 & B2
    B1 --> B3
    B2 --> B3
    B3 --> C0
    C0 --> C1 & C2
    C1 & C2 --> C3
    C3 --> E1 & E2 & E3 & E4 & E5
    E1 --> D1
    D1 --> D2 & D3
    D2 & D3 --> C0 & C1 & C2
```

### Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology | Why |
|---|---|---|
| **Data Pipeline** | Apache Airflow + dbt | Scheduled batch ETL with mode-specific transforms |
| **Feature Store** | Feast / Redis | Fast feature retrieval; separate feature groups per mode |
| **Carrier Scoring** | Scikit-learn, XGBoost | Interpretable, production-ready |
| **Ocean-Specific** | LSTM (PyTorch) | Port congestion needs sequential modeling |
| **Rate Forecasting** | Prophet / NeuralProphet | Time-series with seasonality (ocean peak season, air pre-holiday surges) |
| **Optimization** | Google OR-Tools / PuLP | Best-in-class for mixed-integer programming |
| **Bid Parsing** | Gemini / GPT-4 API | Handles PDFs, emails, Excel bids in any mode's format |
| **Explainability** | SHAP + LIME | Model-agnostic; works across all mode-specific models |
| **Backend** | FastAPI (Python) | High-performance async API |
| **Frontend** | React + D3.js / Recharts | Interactive cross-modal dashboards |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL + TimescaleDB | Relational + time-series for rate/performance history |
| **Real-time Data** | Kafka / Redis Streams | Ingest vessel AIS, flight status, truck GPS |
| **Deployment** | Docker + Kubernetes | Scalable; each "brain" as a separate microservice |

