| **Transit Expense** | Baseline | **20% reduction** via cross-modal optimization | ResearchGate simulated results |
| **Bid Processing** | 1 analyst / 50 bids/day (single mode) | **500+ bids auto-processed** across all modes | LLM-powered parsing |
