| **Award Consistency** | Varies by analyst & mode | **100% standardized** — same methodology across all modes | Eliminates tribal knowledge |

### ROI Model (Illustrative)

For a company with **₹200 Cr annual multi-modal freight spend**:
- **Modal shift optimization** (air → rail for 15% of volume) = ₹8–12 Cr savings
- **Within-mode carrier optimization** (5% avg across modes) = ₹10 Cr savings
- **Reduced delays & penalties** (predictive risk avoidance) = ₹3–5 Cr
- **Procurement team productivity** (80% time reduction) = capacity for strategic initiatives

